Prowl nods, letting go of Dinobot's jaw and looking at Iron Raptor. He looks 
her over, noting that she was covered with mechfluid.

The bot, madly in love with her, walks up to her, glancing at Dinobot.

"So, what's been going on while I was being repaired, love?"
